---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

---

<BaseLayout title="About - Nivedita Pandey">
  <article class="about">
    <h1>Bio</h1>

    <div class="bio-banner">
      <img
        src="/images/hero-professional.png"
        alt="Nivedita Pandey"
        class="bio-banner-img"
      />
    </div>

    <section class="bio">
      <p>
        I build products, platforms, verticals, and strategic initiatives at the intersection of technology, business, and impact - and I've done it across the public and private sector, from fintech to central bank innovation, from luxury consumer goods to government AI.
      </p>
      <p>
        I have founded Microsoft's PE/VC partnerships vertical across APAC and scaled it to $130M, built Asia's first digital gold fintech from zero to $124M GMV, served as a Prime Minister's Fellow on Digital Public Infrastructure where my implementation ranked #1 in India ahead of Delhi, and advised the Reserve Bank Innovation Hub on AI and global growth.
      </p>
      <p>
        I hold an MBA from Wharton as a Joseph Wharton Fellow, a Computer Science degree with distinction where I ranked 1st in a class of 600, and a Masters from IRMA where I ranked 1st in the All-India entrance among tens of thousands of students.
      </p>
      <p>
        I currently run Dendrons.ai, an agentic AI company supported by Google Cloud for Startups and on path to the Anthropic Partner Network.
      </p>

      <p class="bio-contact">
        <a href="mailto:NiveditaPandey@alumni.upenn.edu">NiveditaPandey@alumni.upenn.edu</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 750px;
  }

  .about h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .bio-banner {
    width: 100%;
    height: 520px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .bio-banner-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 20%;
    display: block;
  }

  .bio p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bio p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .domains-intro {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem !important;
  }

  .work-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .work-list li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .work-list strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .bio-values {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary) !important;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .bio-contact {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .bio-contact a {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .bio-banner {
      height: 220px;
    }
  }
</style>
